Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:54.00,BGS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}{\fnArial}Anfang der bewegung
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.80,BGS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}{\fnArial}Anfang des nerven anschlusses
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.80,BGS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}{\fnArial}Auslöses von links-kleigung
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.10,BGS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}{\fnArial}Sychro start
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}错误？怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}思考杂讯，不是叫你别妨碍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你在用日语思考吧，要用德语思考才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}年…年轮蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.40,BGS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}{\fnArial}B…Baumkuchen…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}算了，真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}思考语言切换，以日语为基础
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}EVANGELION 二号机，启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}奥赛罗号（Othello）来电，EVA 二号机正在启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}好样的，明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不行，启动终止，快恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}别管他明日香，快点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}EVA 与驾驶员都在我们的管辖内，不许你们乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}说什么啊？都这种时候了还管什么程序不程序的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不过是认真的吗？二号机仍是 B 装备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}掉到海里就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不掉下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真嗣也在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}两个小孩在上面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}值得一试…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}明日香，开出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}在哪
