Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}只剩 58 秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我知道
